== I vincoli di dati ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
These constraints specify the numerical distances between two points, and angles between two lines.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Distances and angles ===
</div>

